title: YouTube says it will be less safe for kids under Australia's social media ban
description: The Google-owned platform says parental controls will be stripped away as a result of the ban.
content:
YouTube says Australia's "rushed" new laws to block teens from its platform will mean children will be less safe as its "robust parental controls" will be stripped away.
